---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume - Sagnik Chakraborty" description="Resume for Sagnik Chakraborty with download link.">
  <section class="space-y-8">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Resume</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Sagnik Chakraborty</h1>
        <p class="text-[var(--muted)]">Engineer focused on systems, security, and expressive interfaces.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a class="rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--bg)] shadow-glow transition hover:-translate-y-0.5" href="/resume.pdf" download>
          Download PDF
        </a>
        <a
          class="rounded-full border border-[var(--border)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--text)] transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--accent)]"
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sagnik-chakraborty2112/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]/80 p-6 shadow-card">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Summary</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
          Software engineer working across object-oriented development, DevOps, and security-minded infrastructure. I like creating data-driven applications, hardening systems, and keeping docs/runs reproducible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]/80 p-6 shadow-card lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-1">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Contact</p>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] resume-contact-links">
          <p>🔗 <a class="text-[var(--accent)] hover:underline" href="mailto:sagnikchakraborty212@gmail.com">Email</a></p>
          <p>📧 <a class="text-[var(--accent)] hover:underline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sagnik-chakraborty2112/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></p>
          <p>💻 <a class="text-[var(--accent)] hover:underline" href="https://github.com/RedFlame2112" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]/80 p-6 shadow-card lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-2">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Skills & Technical Tools</p>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--accent)]">Snapshot</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-[var(--muted)]">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Programming Languages</p>
            <p>Golang, C/C++, Java, Rust, Python, Perl, SQL, Lua, JavaScript, C#, PowerShell, OCaml</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Technologies</p>
            <p>Git, PyTorch, TensorFlow, GreenGrass, Azure, GCP, AWS, Splunk, Snyk, Apache Spark, ESXi, Proxmox, Docker, Kubernetes, Terraform, neo4j, Unix, Linux, GDB, EMACS, Windows, x64dbg, Wireshark, tcpdump, Snort, IDA Pro, Ghidra, Radar2, Jadx, CyberChef</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Other Skills</p>
            <p>AI/ML design & development, operating systems, distributed systems, DevOps, vulnerability management, cybersec & offensive testing, data science/analytics, mathematics, communication, teamwork.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]/80 p-6 shadow-card space-y-5 resume-experience lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-3">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Experience</p>
          <span class="text-xs text-[var(--accent)] uppercase tracking-[0.12em]">Selected</span>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/50 p-4 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[var(--accent)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Healthcare Product Consulting - Software Development/Architecture Intern</h3>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">Jun 2023 - Aug 2023</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--accent)]">Cognizant Technology Solutions</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
            <li>Designed and unit tested C# data mapping workflows converting healthcare claims (Facets DB) to HL7 FHIR, improving accuracy by 25%.</li>
            <li>Deployed secure, cost-efficient infrastructure on Kubernetes & Docker; automated CI/CD with Azure DevOps, cutting deployment time.</li>
            <li>Integrated Snyk for real-time vuln detection to safeguard sensitive information across thousands of FACETS users.</li>
            <li>Independently identified pipeline bottlenecks and shipped process improvements that reduced time-to-market for finance-grade data systems.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/50 p-4 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[var(--accent)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Administrator & Infrastructure Developer</h3>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">Jan 2021 - Current</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--accent)]">SIGPwny (ACM @ Illinois)</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
            <li>Managed and optimized 4 ESXi platforms serving 100+ active users; reduced incident response time by 40% and improved availability.</li>
            <li>Designed MicroPython badge PCBs for FallCTF 2023/2024 (~300 people), incorporating reverse engineering and debugging exercises.</li>
            <li>Configured and deployed CTF challenge infrastructure on GKE with focus on network traffic analysis and secure deployment.</li>
            <li>Produced and maintained weekly content and org records; managed media for 600+ YouTube subscribers.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/50 p-4 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[var(--accent)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Cofounder, Purple Team</h3>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">Aug 2024 - Current</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--accent)]">SIGPwny (ACM @ Illinois)</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
            <li>Provisioned and secured OVH cloud and Proxmox environments for purple team operations, including attack/defense exercises for ~30 people.</li>
            <li>Led reverse engineering, penetration testing, and malware analysis during security assessments and CTF events.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/50 p-4 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-[var(--accent)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">CTF Lead</h3>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">Jan 2024 - Current</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--accent)]">SIGPwny (ACM @ Illinois)</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)]">
            <li>Developed STARVE—automated MITRE EMB3D-based embedded attack simulation/vuln testing platform; reduced manual testing by ~30%.</li>
            <li>Led automated attack methods for MITRE eCTF2023; improved team process via structured reverse engineering and security assessments.</li>
            <li>Secured 2nd place overall at MITRE eCTF2024 as a key member for embedded team; demonstrated advanced penetration testing.</li>
            <li>Authored detailed design reports and implemented GitHub issue tracking to streamline project management and collaborative vuln testing.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]/80 p-6 shadow-card lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-2">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Education</p>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-[var(--muted)]">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/40 p-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
              <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign - Champaign, IL</p>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">Expected: May 2027</span>
            </div>
            <p class="italic">M.C.S. - Computer Science</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/40 p-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
              <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign - Champaign, IL</p>
              <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--muted)]">Graduated: May 2025</span>
            </div>
            <p class="italic">B.S. - Computer Engineering</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--card)]/80 p-6 shadow-card lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-3">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[var(--muted)]">Projects</p>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/40 p-3">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shadow-glow" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">GRADAR NIDS</p>
              <p class="text-[var(--muted)]">Gradient-based anomaly scoring on Zeek flow data for network intrusion detection.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/40 p-3">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shadow-glow" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Depth-aware Neural Style Transfer</p>
              <p class="text-[var(--muted)]">CS445 final: MiDaS v3 depth + VGG19 style transfer with depth-dependent masks, tuned layer strengths, and blending to preserve foreground detail.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)]/70 bg-[var(--bg)]/40 p-3">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--accent)] shadow-glow" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">dupedbyte.dev</p>
              <p class="text-[var(--muted)]">Astro + Tailwind site with Markdown content, Shiki highlighting, and Pagefind-ready search.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .resume-contact-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.3rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: color 180ms ease, text-shadow 180ms ease, background-color 180ms ease;
  }

  .resume-contact-links a:hover,
  .resume-contact-links a:focus-visible,
  .resume-contact-links a:active {
    color: var(--text);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(231, 243, 234, 0.35);
    background-color: rgba(231, 243, 234, 0.06);
  }

  @media (hover: none) {
    .resume-contact-links a {
      touch-action: manipulation;
    }
  }
</style>
